frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased latency in ProductCatalogService/GetProduct calls\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal duration ~11ms vs anomaly ~14ms. Observed in multiple nodes, occurrences range from 9 to 13.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High latency detected in EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation and PaymentService/Charge\",\n      \"evidence\": \"SendOrderConfirmation average increased from ~20ms to ~88ms, while PaymentService/Charge spiked to ~66s\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "从指标分析数据中，我们可以看到以下几个显著异常：\n\n### 异常指标分析\n1. **服务级别异常**:\n   - **`productcatalogservice-0`**:\n     - `request` 和 `response` 的 `median_change_ratio` 均超过 1.9，指示该服务请求和响应时间急剧下降。\n   - **`frontend-0`**:\n     - `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 的 `median_change_ratio` 高达 2.0，指示此服务的错误率严重增加，影响用户请求的成功率。\n   - **`recommendationservice-0`**:\n     - `rrt_max` 的 `p99_change_ratio` 接近 2.0，这表明该服务的响应时间最大值急剧上升，影响整体性能。\n\n2. **Pod级别异常**:\n   - **`frontend-1`** 和 **`productcatalogservice-0`**:\n     - `pod_cpu_usage` 显示为 0，表明该 Pod 可能根本没有在运行，影响服务的处理能力。\n\n### 关键指标提取\n提取绝对值变化最显著的指标:\n- `[\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"]`\n\n### 异常原因和影响组件\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Degradation in request and response timings with high change ratios indicating service instability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"request ratio increased from normal median of 12448.0 to 199.0, indicating service request performance drop. Same for response ratio increasing from 10464.0 to 173.5.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant rise in error ratios signals potential service failures impacting user requests.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio change from normal median 0 to fault median 15.13, with a change ratio of 2.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Max response time drastically increased indicating potential performance bottlenecks or failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from normal median 21802.0 to 9006.0, with a fault p99 of 684997721.73 showing massive anomalies.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上分析为初步扫描阶段的结果，下一步可能需要深入的协议层面分析或系统日志审查，以确定细节的根因。"}
